  "original_title": "\u0d85\u0da9\u0dd4 \u0d86\u0daf\u0dcf\u0dba\u0db8\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dcf\u0db7\u0dd3\u0db1\u0dca\u0da7 \u0daf\u0dd4\u0db1\u0dca \u0db1\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dcf\u0dc3 22,000\u0d9a\u0da7 \u0d94\u0db4\u0dca\u0db4\u0dd4 \u0db1\u0dd1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "22,000 houses given to low-income earners have no deeds",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Prasanna Ranatunga, Minister of Urban Development and Housing, said that 22,308 home beneficiaries of the low-income housing projects provided by the government have not been given title deeds so far.",
        "The minister also said that the number of houses given to low-income earners by the Urban Development Authority, National Housing Development Authority and Urban Settlement Development Authority under the Ministry of Urban Development and Housing is 32,933, of which title deeds have been given to only 10,625 house owners. said.",
        "The minister also mentioned that he instructed the authorities to issue title deeds to the home beneficiaries within the next one year.",
        "The minister said that he instructed to resolve the issue of the deeds by September 31 at the institutional level and to amend the ordinances if necessary.",
        "The minister mentioned this while attending a discussion held at the Ministry of Urban Development and Housing auditorium in Setsiripay, Battaramulla.",
        "The minister said that it is the responsibility of the concerned institution to give the title deed to the home owners as soon as possible and said that President Ranil Wickramasinghe had emphasized in the policy statement presented to the Parliament recently that the title deeds will be given to the Dattattu house owners in an expedited manner.",
        "He said that the President's Secretary has also appointed a committee of 11 members to get recommendations to solve the problems in giving title deeds to flat house owners and home beneficiaries who have not received title deeds."
      ],
